"content": "<style>\nh1.thlex-title { font-size: 1.3em; margin: 0 0 0.4em; }\n.thlex-key { color: #888; font-size: 0.85em; font-weight: normal; margin-right: 0.4em; }\nnav.thlex-index { margin: 0.5em 0 0.75em; }\nnav.thlex-index ul { margin: 0; padding-left: 1.2em; }\nnav.thlex-index li { margin: 0.15em 0; font-size: 0.95em; }\n.thlex-section { margin: 0.6em 0; }\nh2.thlex-heading { font-size: 1em; margin: 0.5em 0 0.2em; }\nh3.thlex-subheading { font-size: 0.95em; font-weight: normal; font-style: italic; margin: 0.2em 0; }\n.thlex-language-sets { margin: 0.3em 0 0.3em 1em; }\n.thlex-language-set { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 0.75em; border-left: 3px solid #e0e0e0; }\n.thlex-language { font-size: 0.8em; color: #888; margin-right: 0.4em; }\n.thlex-lemma { font-weight: bold; font-family: serif; }\n.thlex-translit { color: #555; font-style: italic; font-size: 0.9em; margin-left: 0.3em; }\n.thlex-refs { font-size: 0.85em; color: #444; margin-top: 0.15em; }\n.thlex-paragraphs p { margin: 0.35em 0; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.5; }\n.thlex-image { margin: 0.5em 0; }\n.thlex-image img { max-width: 100%; height: auto; }\n.thlex-abbr { border-bottom: 1px dotted #888; cursor: help; }\n.thlex-xref { color: #1a5fb4; }\nspan[data-bnType=\"bibleReference\"] { color: #1a5fb4; }\ntable.thlex-table { border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 0.9em; margin: 0.5em 0; }\ntable.thlex-table td { padding: 0.2em 0.6em; vertical-align: top; border: 1px solid #ddd; }\ntable.thlex-table tr:first-child td { font-weight: bold; background: #f5f5f5; }\nul.thlex-index-list { margin: 0.4em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; font-size: 0.95em; line-height: 1.6; }\nul.thlex-index-list ul { margin: 0.1em 0; padding-left: 1.4em; }\n.thlex-index-key { font-weight: bold; font-style: italic; }\n</style><h1 class=\"thlex-title\" id=\"FAUNA:2.16.1\"><span class=\"thlex-key\">2.16.1</span> 標題：小山羊（young goat, kid）</h1><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">經文出處</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-sets\">\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Hebrew</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">來：גְּדִי, גְּדִיָּה</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：gedi, gediyah)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:9\">GEN 27:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen27:16\">GEN 27:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:17\">GEN 38:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:20\">GEN 38:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen38:23\">GEN 38:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:19\">EXO 23:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod34:26\">EXO 34:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut14:21\">DEU 14:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:19\">JDG 6:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:15\">JDG 13:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg13:19\">JDG 13:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg14:6\">JDG 14:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg15:1\">JDG 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam10:3\">1SA 10:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam16:20\">1SA 16:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:8\">SNG 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:6\">ISA 11:6</a></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"thlex-language-set\">\n<span class=\"thlex-language\">Greek</span> <span class=\"thlex-lemma\">希：ἔριφος, ἐρίφιον</span> <span class=\"thlex-translit\">(音譯：erifos, erifion)</span>\n<div class=\"thlex-refs\"><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:32\">MAT 25:32</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:33\">MAT 25:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:29\">LUK 15:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob2:12\">TOB 2:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Tob2:13\">TOB 2:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Sir47:3\">SIR 47:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Esd1:7\">1ES 1:7</a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">討論</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p><figure class=\"thlex-image\"><img class=\"thlex-img\" src=\"images/WEB-0264_goat_kid.jpg\" alt=\"WEB-0264_goat_kid\"></figure>以色列人通常只在特殊的節期宰殺肥牛犢，但是會定期宰殺肥山羊羔（包括公的和母的）作平常食用。公山羊只有在成年之後，其肉質才會因為性成熟而帶有很重的膻味。</p>\n</div>\n</div><div class=\"thlex-section\">\n<h2 class=\"thlex-heading\">翻譯</h2>\n<div class=\"thlex-paragraphs\">\n<p>在希伯來文中，<em>gedi</em> 經常與其他表示山羊的詞（如<em>‘ez</em> ）一起使用，形成類似<em>gedi ‘izim</em> 的表達，字面意思是「山羊的小羊」。這個較長表達和詞語<em>gedi</em> 的意思完全相同。在所有經文中，翻譯者都可以使用一個具體的詞語或者表示小山羊或幼崽的短語。參上一個條目中的插圖。</p>\n</div>\n</div>",
